name: Luna's Uekura Eku Style Lora
description:
Trained on artwork by the artist Uekura Eku(上倉エク) on pixiv.

Can it do nudes? Yes... Can it do lewds? Yes.

As always, I pruned images that were too far from the target style.

This artist only really draws characters floating in white voids, so at high weights you will probably get poses that arent quite right. Their style is very pastel and light, so the colors will reflect that. They do chaotic backgrounds, so expect a lot of wacky details. Their style is more a cute flat chested look, and without a chest size specified it will always produce that. But as shown, it can do any size you wish.

Does the trigger word matter? No not really, I have included an example of the variance between the trigger words at the end. But I'm adding lunachan to all my lora so you can always just use that for everything.

Some images included highresfix, I typically user under 0.6, and lollypop/4X animesharp. I did not use any other lora in combination with this. DPM++ 2M Karras is my sampler of choice.
